{"tid":1475851,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[重要][點解要去818]休班公務員都出聲了！","createTime":"2019-08-15T15:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T05:30:03.000Z","uid":113148,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1df22a4146acdccdbdb1445e5814b1b017a03d82","tid":1475851,"uid":113148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:23:04.000Z","msg":"朋友係公務員，有少少野想講:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>818遊行對我地以至政府，甚至世界而言，係一個重要既民意指標，體現兩個月以來即民意變化。和理非同勇武只係行動時既特質。<ins>每個人，都會有做理理非同勇武行為既時候。</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府同黑警喺過往清場犯左咁多規，極需要我地以最文明既手段，做一次<strong><em>單向既譴責</em></strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係，以身作則盡力展現零失誤，避免一切挑釁或者衝突，，屌打藍絲/淺黃覺行每場大遊行必然出現衝突收場既負面印象，用文明大大力錫政府春袋！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求下大家，發生咁多事，香港人好善忘、好崇拜&quot;理性討論&quot;，所以更加需要一個和平收尾既大遊行。如果今次成功，會<ins>擲地有聲</ins>咁展示香港人唔會被仇恨掩蓋理智，同時會係大部分人既定心丸！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n612 721 811<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n818 維園見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eun0Ane.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEun0Ane.jpg&h=a3a48eae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yon7ZOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyon7ZOU.jpg&h=4aed31ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oUbTVne.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoUbTVne.jpg&h=2ffc55b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LqKaXAA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLqKaXAA.jpg&h=0f263e88&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BpbTVnf.png\" data-thumbnail-